data.description: Welcome home, you will enjoy spending time in the large manicured backyard relaxing or entertaining. The inviting tile flooring runs from the front door throughout to the backdoor, creating an expansive space.  All can gather around the kitchen that opens up to the family area and a conveniently located office space that displays double french doors.  The master bedroom hosts plush carpet with endless space, private bathroom accented with a walk in shower and walk in closet. The remaining bedrooms are generous in size and the home features 3 refrigeration units perfect for those hot summer days. This is a must to see, ready to move-in.
